text: Asavo-Zubovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kazadayevsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 137 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 14 km from Sterlitamak, 4 km from Novoye Baryatino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Asavo-Zubovo
